# Agentic AI Projects Roadmap

Mastering Agentic AI does not come from reading SDK documentation.

It comes from building increasingly capable systems.

The goal of these projects is to move through:

```text
Tool Calling
    ↓
Agent Loops
    ↓
Memory
    ↓
Multi-Agent Systems
    ↓
Production Agents
    ↓
Autonomous Workflows
```

By the end, you should be able to build systems comparable to:

* Claude Code
* Cursor Agent
* Deep Research Agents
* Customer Support Agents
* Knowledge Workers
* Multi-Agent Enterprise Systems

---

