# Mastery Signals

## Beginner

* [ ] Can define tools
* [ ] Can execute tool calls
* [ ] Can build simple agents

---

## Intermediate

* [ ] Can build agent loops
* [ ] Can manage memory
* [ ] Can use retrieval systems

---

## Advanced

* [ ] Can build coding agents
* [ ] Can build research agents
* [ ] Can design multi-agent systems

---

## Expert

* [ ] Can build production voice agents
* [ ] Can deploy autonomous workflows
* [ ] Can design enterprise agent architecture

---

## Architect

* [ ] Can build Claude Code clone
* [ ] Can build Deep Research clone
* [ ] Can design multi-agent platforms
* [ ] Can build agent infrastructure used by other engineers
* [ ] Can reason about safety, observability, reliability, and cost at scale

